  "description": "<i>The Zacaron Mystery</i> is a traditional text adventure made using the Quill adventure generation software from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Gilsoft\">Gilsoft</a>. You tell the game what you want to do via a textual interface and the parser is based on a verb / noun input.<br><br>The year is 3065 and Earth's fuel reserves will only last a few more months. The only solution is to find two Zacaron crystals on the distant planets of Prutor and Myra. You play the role of a skilled interstellar pilot that is sent to retrieve the crystals.",
